description:
Was Joker the sequel we hoped it would be, or did it crash and burn? And now that ROP is finally over, what did we think of it? Join me, Ryan Kinel, Chris Gore, The Movie Cynic and George The Giant Slayer as we find out.

title: Open Bar #114 - Joker 2, Rings of Power Ends, Agatha Sucks
